org.mindroid.android.app.robodancer

Class DefaultRobotPortConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mindroid.android.app.robodancer.DefaultRobotPortConfig

  • public class DefaultRobotPortConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Default configuration of Sensor/sensormodes and Motors of the Robot. Gets used by the SettingsProvider SettingsProvider when loading the setup from the SharedPreferences xml file. If this file does not contain any information about a port or the whole setup it will load the default values from this class.
